<title>HONG KONG: C.Lyonnais sets call warrants on red-chip basket.</title>
<headline>C.Lyonnais sets call warrants on red-chip basket.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-01-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Lyonnais Financial Products (Guernsey) Ltd said on Friday it has launched 380 million American-style call warrants on a basket of red chips.</p>
<p>Each basket comprises:</p>
<p> China Resources Beijing Land Ltd	  0.3 shares</p>
<p> CITIC Pacific Ltd			     0.1 shares</p>
<p> Guangnan (Holdings) Ltd		     0.3 shares</p>
<p> GZI Transport Ltd			     0.3 shares</p>
<p> Top Glory International Holdings Ltd    1.0 shares</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one basket.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	HK$10.7625     PREMIUM	   21.8 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	 HK$0.2346	GEARING	   4.59x</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	  30.JAN.98	EXER LOT	  10,000</p>
<p> LISTING	     HONG KONG	PAYDATE	   03.MAR.97</p>
<p> REFERENCE SPOT    HK$10.7625     LISTING DATE    05.MAR.97</p>
<p> GOVERNING LAW     HONG KONG</p>
<p> NOTE		  CASH SETTLEMENT OR PHYSICAL DELIVERY AT</p>
<p>			 ISSUER'S DISCRETION</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
</text>
